data.description: Charming Cape Cod Home featuring 3-bedrooms and 2 full baths. This all-brick Cape Cod home seamlessly blends classic charm with modern updates. Hardwood floors throughout, a modern kitchen with stainless appliances and granite countertops, and abundance of natural light creating a warm and inviting space. Recent 2020 updates include new windows, roof, HVAC, gutters and main plumbing to keep that peace of mind and energy efficiency. The large backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, and the open floor plan enhances the home's spacious feel. This home is a timeless gem worth exploring, so schedule your showing today.
